survey_response.review_text: Friendly doctor. Explains any issue with ease. Will surely recommend her to anyone. The clinic is also well maintained and hygienic.

*** ** *** **** ******* **** ****** ***** ********* *** understanding. 
Nice experience... Will recommend you guys to go for any dental solution. 
Just want to share my overall experience. 
"I got my dental filling done by her and she did a great job.. Unfortunately the filling cane out due to my mistake.. When I spoke to her without any hesitation the told me to come back to her and she fixed my tooth without even charging me."
So it's  not about I got it fixed for free it's about a Doctor who cares for the patient and not the other way round.

*** ******** ** ** *** *** **** ******* * **** *** *****

she is so polite and helpful, and so cheerful and caring to her patients. 

I had got Root Canal Treatment done from her, and both she and I know how much pain i had. She has been really careful in doing the treatment throughout and made sure I dont get any pain at all.

I have absolutely no doubt in recommending Dr. Sulochna as your family Dentist at all, as she is so good at it, and her work would always speak for her and you would feel the same after getting your treatments done too.

I would like to thank Dr. Sulochna again for helping me through the pain, and also helping me up even on the weekend by staying longer than your usual timings just to make sure that I dont get any pain through the rest of the day.

5 stars out of 5 is just not enough for a Dentist like her :)

*** ** *** **** ******* * **** **** **** ******* She will do the treatment till the time the problem get fully resolved irrespective of enormous time. She don't bother for money, patient satisfaction is her priority. She is perfect Dr.I will definitely recommend every one who has a dental issue to visit her.She will treat really well.

survey_response.review_text:
I went to get for a very small assistance after my tooth extraction done out of Bangalore.
I was charged quite high for the service needed.

I had visited Dr. Sulochana for root canal . I was initially skeptical about the treatment thinking about the pain involved and all.
Doctor was really professional and explained about the complete process.The pain was minimal and after the treatment everything was normal.
I would definitely recommend Dr Sulochana for your dental treatments

I had a toothache and visited Dr. Sulochana in Sep'21 , she diagnosed the issue correctly and patiently heard by problem. What seemed to be a minor tooth filing treatment was actually a very fine cracked tooth which was causing the pain. This and other complexity involved, she advised for the Root canal treatment and after few appointments the treatment was completed. 

I am thankful for the timely and ******** diagnosis and strongly recommend her service.

Dr. Sulochana is a very friendly doctor and listens to your dental issues in detail and addresses all issues to your satisfaction. I've been consulting her for a few years now and I have only positive feedback for her. She is very professional and explains post care instructions very patiently. My family members have also been consulting her for any kind of dental issues and are extremely satisfied with her dental care.

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you so much Nitin Jain😊

survey_response.review_text: we went to doctor with mindset of root-canal treatment but after thorough examination doctor suggested that root-canal is not required and just cleaning-filling-restoration should be enough & it really worked. we like diagnosis & treatment quality. On top of everything Honesty of doctor is really great. we are in the era where people are doing anything for INR But doctor Sulochana treated in minimum cost with high quality & avoided unnecessary costly treatments. Thanks dr. Sulochana.

I visited SK Dental for treatment of severe tooth sensitivity and pain. Dr. Sulochana advised me to go for dental crown. I liked her integrity. Rather than going for RCT she saved my original teeth with the dental crown. *** ** **** ******* **** *** *********** amazingly punctual and very friendly with the patients. 
Highly recommended.
